1
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:48,100
=Dark and Dawn=
(The Unique Her: Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:50,420
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:52,740 --> 00:00:53,740
Do you really want me

4
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:54,940
to call you Dad?

5
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,980
I don't think I've ever said that word.

6
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,660
Ever since I was born,

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:05,500
I've hated you to this day.

8
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:09,540
Maybe I should just keep hating you.

9
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:14,460
Xiao'ai hasn't accepted you either.

10
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:18,660
Maybe she will later.

11
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:21,980
Maybe she never will.

12
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:25,140
You deserve it.

13
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:51,860
Either be a good dad in your next life

14
00:01:53,860 --> 00:01:55,380
or don't have us at all.

15
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:04,500
You failed to protect me,

16
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:06,580
so I'll protect myself.

17
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:09,980
If you can,

18
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,460
please watch over Xiao'ai from heaven

19
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:17,260
and let her always live in the light.

20
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,220
Honey,

21
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:20,100
I've been waiting for you to come home.

22
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:38,860
Didn't you say you'd die for me?

23
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:41,260
You really want me dead?

24
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:42,540
Don't worry.

25
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:45,660
If you die, I'll pay with my life.

26
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:50,740
You're crazy.

27
00:03:52,660 --> 00:03:53,500
I am.

28
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:56,300
How else could I fall for you?

29
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:01,140
Li Jin, are you afraid to die?

30
00:04:01,660 --> 00:04:03,300
I know you're trash.

31
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:06,300
I didn't expect you to be such a loser.

32
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,140
What a coward.

33
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,260
You're scared to die.

34
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:19,620
But I'm not.

35
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:25,540
Lili!

36
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,500
Lili!

37
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:34,220
You promised to die with me.

38
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:35,860
Does that still count?

39
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:05,980
Lili...

40
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,340
Lili!

41
00:05:31,340 --> 00:05:32,300
Lili!

42
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:34,740
Lili!

43
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:35,660
Wake up!

44
00:05:39,180 --> 00:05:40,020
Hello?

45
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:41,660
Lili!

46
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:43,020
Don't scare me!

47
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,620
Lili!

48
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,340
Lili...

49
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:05,780
Lili!

50
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:07,620
Lili!

51
00:06:12,460 --> 00:06:13,740
Why am I here?

52
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,260
Lili.

53
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,180
You've been out for a day.

54
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,380
You're very weak right now.

55
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:27,020
I've gotten the best doctor.

56
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,020
She'll be fine.

57
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,580
She's my sister.

58
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,340
She's my best friend.

59
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:33,422
If anything happens to her,

60
00:06:33,433 --> 00:06:34,660
I could never forgive myself.

61
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,220
I couldn't even protect her.

62
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,780
Calm down.

63
00:06:38,380 --> 00:06:39,220
Don't worry.

64
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,620
I won't let anything happen to her.

65
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:43,540
Trust me.

66
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:45,900
Okay?

67
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:53,620
Uncle,

68
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:56,900
I've already lost my mom.

69
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,260
I can't lose my sister too.

70
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:04,300
You were very brave.

71
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,340
You saved her.

72
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,540
Get some sleep.

73
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:24,940
You need to rest.

74
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:29,900
I can't sleep.

75
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:32,460
Every time I close my eyes,

76
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:35,500
all I see is Lili covered in blood.

77
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:40,860
Lili will get better.

78
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:45,060
And you will too.

79
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:49,740
Is everyone I love

80
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:53,540
going to leave me?

81
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:57,700
I'm right here.

82
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,260
I'll always be by your side.

83
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:23,700
It's time.

84
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:35,500
Time for what?

85
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:38,700
Ms. Li, it's time for the meeting.

86
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:43,900
Ms. Li, have some water.

87
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:51,540
(Zhuang Lili, bloom like a flower)

88
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:52,380
Zhuang Lili?

89
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:55,660
Do I know her?

90
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,100
You do.

91
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,300
Is she a girl?

92
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,220
She's a very beautiful girl.

93
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:17,820
(Zhuang Lili, bloom like a flower)

94
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,020
(Zhuang Lili, bloom like a flower)

95
00:10:24,020 --> 00:10:25,180
Actually, Li Jin

96
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:27,380
lost his parents at a young age.

97
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:29,460
The more insecure he feels,

98
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,780
the more he wants to control everything.

99
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:33,780
But that's no excuse

100
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,300
for all the bad things he's done.

101
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:38,300
People always have

102
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:39,900
to pay for their actions.

103
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:43,260
Goodbye

104
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:44,660
to the old me.

105
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:48,420
It's all over.

106
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:51,620
Let's go.

107
00:11:24,900 --> 00:11:25,740
Mom,

108
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:28,460
I came to see you.

109
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:35,700
This is my best friend,

110
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,540
Xiao'ai.

111
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,160
♪Get ready♪

112
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,960
♪To leave this troubled world behind♪

113
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:08,880
♪Say goodbye to the past♪

114
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,280
♪Waiting♪

115
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,920
♪No more secrets hidden in my heart♪

116
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,600
♪To discover♪

117
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:19,160
♪Love is unfolding♪

118
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:23,000
♪Wind softly blows to the dazzling sky♪

119
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:27,760
♪Chasing the endless blue sky♪

120
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:31,520
♪I won't be trapped in a single moment♪

121
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:34,480
♪Trying to change♪

122
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,880
♪Roaming the whole world♪

123
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:41,280
♪Gentle breeze on my face♪

124
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:45,840
♪Fresh thoughts fill the air♪

125
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,800
♪Stars after the dark♪

126
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:51,880
♪Lost in wonder beneath the stars♪

127
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:55,360
♪Love slowly arrives♪

128
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:04,800
♪Declaring freedom in every moment♪

129
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:10,320
♪An endless adventure ahead♪

130
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:13,680
♪Always transforming♪
